{
  "text": "To get a deep understanding of the effect of customer loyalty programs on customer retention, the study of [CITATION_1] was connected on Jordanian clients, exploring the effect of loyalty programs: (point system, tier system reward, charges an upfront fee for VIP benefits and nonmonetary programs), on (customer retention) using a survey. The results showed a significant impact of all loyalty programs on building and keeping up customer retention. The major impact was for Tier framework reward followed after by charge Up-front fee for VIP benefits, and after that point frame point system work, the weakest impact was for non-monetary programs omers.",
